And he became the patron saint of Ireland, leading the revival all across the country.

00:50:01.484 --> 00:50:03.306
Christianity flourished and broke out.

00:50:03.326 --> 00:50:08.614
The love of the Word of God, the Book of Kells, and all the story and heritage of St. Patrick is powerful.

00:50:09.515 --> 00:50:11.117
And he only left a couple of writings.

00:50:11.157 --> 00:50:12.679
But what he wrote was so beautiful.

00:50:12.719 --> 00:50:23.314
And I wanted to put on the screen something I would ask for you to speak over your life and to bless yourself and to bless your family and to bless your home and let the sound of this blessing ring out

00:50:24.130 --> 00:50:28.735
for all who hear as we pray this together over ourselves in prayer of St. Patrick.

00:50:29.736 --> 00:50:31.679
May the strength of God pilot me.

00:50:32.420 --> 00:50:34.462
May the power of God preserve me.

00:50:35.203 --> 00:50:37.385
May the wisdom of God instruct me.

00:50:38.026 --> 00:50:39.768
May the hand of God protect me.

00:50:40.489 --> 00:50:42.091
May the way of God direct me.

00:50:42.772 --> 00:50:44.954
May the shield of God defend me.

00:50:45.615 --> 00:50:46.035
Amen.

00:50:46.115 --> 00:50:47.197
God bless you, church.

00:50:47.297 --> 00:50:47.757
Love you.

00:50:47.878 --> 00:50:49.279
May God bless you in great ways.

00:50:49.299 --> 00:50:51.762
Oh, amazing.

00:50:51.874 --> 00:50:53.636
Hey, so we're worshiping still.

00:50:53.656 --> 00:50:54.998
What an amazing time.

00:50:55.619 --> 00:50:56.019
Amazing message.

00:50:56.039 --> 00:51:00.164
Happy St. Patrick's week to all of you, and I pray God's blessing on your life.

00:51:00.184 --> 00:51:09.456
I know this was a charged message to hear, and all of these weeks have been intense, but beautiful, and I'm just believing that God's giving you the strength.

00:51:09.476 --> 00:51:17.746
Even now as you watch this, we're grateful you're a part of this ministry to break free from these generational patterns and sins and to walk in something brand new.

00:51:18.626 --> 00:51:25.859
And a big part of that might be taking a step of faith, and maybe you're watching this and you say, hey, I don't know what God has for me, but I'm sensing a follow-up ministry.

00:51:25.899 --> 00:51:29.506
One thing I would encourage you to do is pray about joining the Fresh Life Leadership College.

00:51:29.526 --> 00:51:30.808
We're taking applications now.

00:51:31.289 --> 00:51:36.599
We'd love to have you pursue a degree, study, and be a part of all the gods doing at Fresh Life.

00:51:36.619 --> 00:51:37.701
Information's on the screen.

00:51:38.121 --> 00:51:39.163
Check it out.

00:51:39.183 --> 00:51:40.626
Well, God bless your church.
